      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/85e7bf/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2018-04-01T22:02:06.961Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Peshqit e medhenj jane hala ne det o Lu efendi por ti bej hazer tiganin <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/blush.png?v=5\" title=\":blush:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":blush:\"></p>",
