    {
      "id": 71419,
      "post_number": 5,
      "username": "xhibi",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/xhibi/{size}/311_2.png",
      "created_at": "2018-04-02T00:54:50.829Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Sot e ka radhen Krishti mer, ta kishim filluar neser apelin per ringjallen peshqve te medhenj. E mbase duhet ta fshehem kete <a href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/t/kush-e-helmoi-peshkun/3901\">ritualin</a> dhe te hapem nje me fryme nostalgjiko-pozitive qe mos tremben. Muzike ne sfond, gurabije Lazarati, lajthi dhe mobilje qe kane zene pluhur strategjikisht.</p>\n<p>Per ndonje specikishit mund te na duhet te negociojme, si p.sh. per ate qí na e mori Trumpi nizam dhe i vuri kapele iMAGA <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/cowboy_hat_face.png?v=5\" title=\":cowboy_hat_face:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":cowboy_hat_face:\"> <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/frowning.png?v=5\" title=\":frowning:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":frowning:\"></p>\n<p>Qa keni bere qekiqa &amp; qekiqe? <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/popcorn.png?v=5\" title=\":popcorn:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":popcorn:\"></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
