      "created_at": "2018-04-02T17:01:58.478Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Xhibi i dashur, ku ke qene gjith keto muaj a vite, klandestin vlla  <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/laughing.png?v=5\" title=\":laughing:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":laughing:\"></p>",
