      "created_at": "2018-04-03T21:40:52.869Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Ne dore te gjykatave</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox whitelistedgeneric\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <a href=\"http://www.gazetatema.net/2018/04/03/bashkia-e-tiranes-gjykata-administrative-i-hap-rruge-ndertimit-te-5-pallateve-17-kateshe-te-diga-e-liqenit-artificial/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"07:33PM - 03 April 2018\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Gazeta Tema – 3 Apr 18</a>\n  </header>\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:800/400;\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/3/300ff3dbca5fc24b88b87f0ff9523bae93ffb566.jpg\" class=\"thumbnail\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.gazetatema.net/2018/04/03/bashkia-e-tiranes-gjykata-administrative-i-hap-rruge-ndertimit-te-5-pallateve-17-kateshe-te-diga-e-liqenit-artificial/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Bashkia e Tiranës: Gjykata Administrative i hap rrugë ndërtimit të 5 pallateve...</a></h3>\n\n<p>Bashkia e Tiranës ka denoncuar Gjykatën Administrative, se ka lejuar ndërtimin e 5 pallateve 17 katëshe tek Diga e Liqenit Artificial.\n\nNjoftimi i Bashkisë\n\nSot, Gjykata Administrative e Apelit, në një mbledhje të pa njoftuar dhe jashtë vëmendjes...</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.gazetadita.al/sot-jepet-vendimi-kryebashiaku-i-lezhes-ne-apel-jam-i-pafajshem/\" class=\"onebox\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">http://www.gazetadita.al/sot-jepet-vendimi-kryebashiaku-i-lezhes-ne-apel-jam-i-pafajshem/</a></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 71716,
      "post_number": 10,
      "username": "kapo",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/kapo/{size}/4005_2.png",
      "created_at": "2018-04-05T00:30:40.851Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Donald Lu na del vete peshk i madh ! <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/joy.png?v=9\" title=\":joy:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":joy:\"></p>\n<p>The U.S. Ambassador to Albania Donald Lu, a holdover from the Obama administration, has been closely linked to Soros and the socialist government in Albania. In May 2017, Lu helped undermine Albanian opposition party plans to protest the upcoming parliamentary election by declaring that the U.S. would recognize the election results even if opposition parties refused to participate. Lu has been described in the U.S. press as “a driving force behind Albania’s judicial reforms.”</p>\n<p>Bie plani marksist per kapjen e reformes ne drejtesi</p>\n<p>Hetimet amerikane rrezojne masakren me reformen ne drejtesi ne Shqiperi dhe nisin hetimet per sponsorizimin e Soros me miliona euro nga taksapaguesit amerikane per ti dhene Rames drejtesine. Abuzuesit drejt burgut.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/8/82192438a9c1a5afcf476a1591e49c4f713712fd.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/82192438a9c1a5afcf476a1591e49c4f713712fd\" title=\"image.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/8/82192438a9c1a5afcf476a1591e49c4f713712fd.jpg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"389\" height=\"800\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/8/82192438a9c1a5afcf476a1591e49c4f713712fd_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">467×960 84 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>",
